profile:
Interior Decorator & CSP certified Home Stager.

ABOUT US
Hi! I'm Kody,

Lead designer and founder here at Kody Kenneth interiors. I am a Georgian College graduate who has always had an passion for home décor and design. As an experienced Interior Decorator and Certified Home Stager I know a thing or two about how to beautify your home and highlight its best features! 

At Kody Kenneth Interiors we use the power of design to transform even the simplest areas into stunning spaces. We enhance interiors using luxury decoration and lifestyle elements. Transforming spaces not only is our business but also what we love to do most. As a result, we have developed a loyal and enthusiastic clientele!
